🖱️ AUTOCLICKER
Randomized CPS between 8-20 with natural click patterns. Auto-block for swords, break blocks while attacking, and inventory management. Looks exactly like legitimate clicking.

🎯 AIMASSIST
Smooth aim tracking with adjustable speed and FOV. Invisible aim correction that feels natural. Perfect for bow aim and melee combat.

🛡️ VELOCITY
